data.description:
Welcome to your own private country paradise! This charming home is situated on 2.2 acres of beautiful and manicured land. The property boasts a spacious barn and storage shed, making it the perfect place to store your tools and equipment. Plus, with multiple covered locations for your vehicles, tractors, or side by sides, you'll have plenty of space for everything you need.

This home would make an excellent AirBnB or hunting cabin. There are already pens in place where the previous owners trained their hunting dogs for weekend hunting retreats. This home is just close enough to town for easy access to grocery stores, etc but far enough away to be out of the hustle and bustle. 

The property is surrounded by beautiful trees, creating an idyllic and peaceful setting that provides plenty of shade and privacy. Additionally, there are multiple areas perfect for a garden that will allow you to grow your own food and enjoy fresh produce year-round.

If you're looking for a beautiful country home with plenty of land and exceptional amenities, look no further than this stunning property. Don't miss your chance to experience the ultimate in rural living!
